snippet.title: Using Peptide Therapy to Reverse Autoimmune Disease, Hormone Imbalances & Low Energy with Dr. Amber
snippet.description:
Peptide therapy is a little-known new emerging treatment in regenerative medicine  that you can do at home to send autoimmune disease into remission, heal chronic pain, boost libido, balance hormones and optimize sleep. Dr. Amber shares all-you-need-to-know about the power of peptides and how to get started.

Bio:

Dr. Amber is a Licensed Naturopathic Doctor at MetroMD Institute of Regenerative Medicine in Los Angeles, CA. She is trained in regenerative medicine, detoxification protocols, hormone testing and treatment, bioidentical hormone therapy, peptide therapy and IV nutrient therapy. She also has a practice in Redondo Beach, CA where she specializes in bioidentical hormones and peptide therapy. Dr. Amber is a member of the International Peptide Society (IPS) and has completed peptide therapy certification training through the American Academy of Anti-aging (A4M).

Website link: www.drambernd.com
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/doctorambernd/
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/groups/peptiderx
